  (text "Telemetry capture notes:\n- Source traces: PB-100-current-telemetry-trace.csv, PB-100-current-telemetry-freeze-review.csv, PB-100-thermal-telemetry-trace.csv, PB-100-thermal-telemetry-freeze-review.csv\n- OUT1_IMON..OUT10_IMON scaled into LB_3V3_IO ADC domain\n- IIN_SENSE total input current path\n- 0.5 mOhm shunt review covers INA228 range, Kelvin sense, ADC/I2C ownership, and calibration config\n- VBAT_SENSE divider\n- TEMP_PCB, TEMP_PWR_A, TEMP_PWR_B use NTC divider/ADC scaling and placement review\n- PB_ID_ADC board identity fallback\n- PB_I2C reserved for digital monitor options\n\nMissing telemetry is a safe fault."
